0_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=l3tNQpNuISYQ7kNvgFFT-qv&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AyoSwR0EeM-9sqbULIjioey&oh=00_AYC13PwP2_A6fHeLG9BHWsiDl8oCACo4k1Mo-E01Q-y3gg&oe=66E2D60B"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "pipes_2560x1440.png", "id": "478124110997892", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974716_478124114331225_7506725568183510468_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=5y03Bp4h7L0Q7kNvgG8UGHo&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AyoSwR0EeM-9sqbULIjioey&oh=00_AYCraZ3AMK-3ZZihGcuIAmZKnen8gkaPZJIPxLh4Zr8YRw&oe=66E2C16C"}, "display_name": "Quack the Pipes!", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Use your plumber powers to place pipes, join the vases and make the water flow!\nHelp little ducks to have fun surfing a water jet! You don't want to sadden a duck...\nBeware, make it in time, or the water will overflow...\n\nReasons to become our favourite plumber:\n\n- You'll be provided with many, many, many Pipes!\n- You'll meet lots of nice ducks, see stunning waterfalls...\n- Puffy clouds will guide you along the way!\n- Positional sounds & music (9 different soundtracks) will relax and alert you when it's time to move!\n- Day, Night and Autumn worlds, for a grand total of 54 challenging levels (and more to come!): hours of challenging gameplay!\n- 2 Game modes : classic, challenge.\n- Challenge your friends with Achievements and Leaderboards!\n- Learn how to plumb and profit in real life!", "short_description": "Use your plumber powers to place pipes, join the vases and make the water flow!\nHelp little ducks to have fun surfing a water jet! You don't want to sadden a duck...\nBeware, make it in time, or the water will overflow..."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://dreamteamgames.net/qtp/privacy-policy.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Zgkaos", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://dreamteamgames.net